com.esp.android.usb.camera.core

Interface IIMUCallback


  • public interface IIMUCallback
    Callback interface for UVCCamera class If you need IMU data by callback, you can use this callback interface with UVCCamera#getIMUData(IIMUCallback callback). This callback also include calibration result.
